PN,43901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778159474
OL,3,CWest Country man one of the first in
OL,4,Cthe UK to receive new cancer jab
OL,6,FWatch: Trevor Garfield describing his
OL,7,F"transformative" experience
OL,9,FA man from Weston-super-Mare is one of
OL,10,Fthe first people in the country to
OL,11,Freceive a new "one-minute" cancer jab.
OL,13,FUniversity Hospitals Bristol and
OL,14,FWeston NHS Foundation Trust (UHBW) is
OL,15,Frolling out a new injection which the
OL,16,FNHS estimates could save more than
OL,17,F100,000 hours of time per year,
OL,18,Fequivalent to around 11 years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778159474
OL,3,CWest Country man one of the first in
OL,4,Cthe UK to receive new cancer jab
OL,6,F79-year-old Trevor Garfield, who has
OL,7,Fbeen receiving the treatment at
OL,8,FBristol Haematology and Oncology
OL,9,FCentre, says the jab has been "truly
OL,10,Famazing" and "transformative".
OL,12,FThe injectable form of pembrolizumab
OL,13,Fcan be administered in one to two
OL,14,Fminutes and can be used to treat 14
OL,15,Fdifferent cancer types, including
OL,16,Flung, head and neck, breast and
OL,17,Fcervical. The UHBW is one of the first
OL,18,Fhospital trusts in the UK to deliver
OL,19,Fit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778159474
OL,3,CWest Country man one of the first in
OL,4,Cthe UK to receive new cancer jab
OL,6,FIt replaces an IV infusion which takes
OL,7,Faround two hours per session, and
OL,8,Ffollows the roll-out of nivolumab,
OL,9,Fanother injectable form of
OL,10,Fimmunotherapy, at UHBW last year.
OL,12,FImmunotherapy treatments such as
OL,13,FPembrolizumab are given over longer
OL,14,Ftimeframes than chemotherapy
OL,15,Fprogrammes, lasting typically one to
OL,16,Ftwo years. It is designed to stimulate
OL,17,Fan immune response from the body to
OL,18,Fkill tumour cells.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778159474
OL,3,CWest Country man one of the first in
OL,4,Cthe UK to receive new cancer jab
OL,6,FMr Garfield said: "The intravenous
OL,7,Ftreatment I received before switching
OL,8,Fto the subcutaneous injection was
OL,9,Fdelivered with great care and
OL,10,Fefficiency but my word!
OL,12,F"The new injection was delivered so
OL,13,Fswiftly that my visit to the hospital
OL,14,Fwas completed in minutes! I was in,
OL,15,Fout and home before you could blink
OL,16,Fand I didn't feel a thing. It was
OL,17,Ftruly amazing!"
OL,26,@nD@SOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778159474
OL,3,CWest Country man one of the first in
OL,4,Cthe UK to receive new cancer jab
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV West Country, he said:
OL,7,F"For myself, it's very convenient to
OL,8,Fbe in and out so quickly. But for
OL,9,Feverybody else who is suffering from
OL,10,Fcancers, it is absolutely terrific."
OL,12,FHe added: "It's so simple and quick
OL,13,Ffor such a nasty disease, it's quite
OL,14,Fincredible."
OL,16,FMr Garfield described his medical team
OL,17,Fas "wonderful", explaining: "It really
OL,18,Fis magnificent, the effort they put
OL,19,Fin."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
