OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778159474
OL,3,CWest Country man one of the first in
OL,4,Cthe UK to receive new cancer jab
OL,6,FThe treatment will be given every
OL,7,Fthree weeks as a one-minute injection
OL,8,For every six weeks as a two-minute
OL,9,Finjection, depending on an
OL,10,Findividual's cancer type. Around
OL,11,F14,000 patients start pembrolizumab
OL,12,Ftherapy each year in England, with
OL,13,Fmost now expected to benefit from the
OL,14,Fmore convenient treatment.
OL,16,FThe NHS says that the time saved will
OL,17,Ffree up vital capacity in pharmacy and
OL,18,Fcancer clinics, allowing teams to
OL,19,Ffocus on preparing and delivering a
OL,20,Fgreater number of more complex cancer
OL,21,Ftherapies.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778159474
OL,3,CWest Country man one of the first in
OL,4,Cthe UK to receive new cancer jab
OL,6,FThe Somerset, Wiltshire, Avon and
OL,7,FGloucestershire (SWAG) Cancer Alliance
OL,8,FClinical Director and Consultant
OL,9,FMedical Oncologist at University
OL,10,FHospitals Bristol and Weston NHS
OL,11,FFoundation Trust, Helen Winter, said:
OL,12,F"Delivering subcutaneous immunotherapy
OL,13,Fcloser to home is a significant step
OL,14,Fforward for patients.
OL,16,F"It reduces the need for repeated and
OL,17,Fprolonged hospital visits while
OL,18,Fmaintaining high-quality care.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778159474
OL,3,CWest Country man one of the first in
OL,4,Cthe UK to receive new cancer jab
OL,6,F"This approach aligns with the
OL,7,FNational Cancer Plan for England,
OL,8,Fwhich highlights the importance of
OL,9,Fshifting more cancer treatment into
OL,10,Fcommunity and home settings.
OL,12,F"We're grateful to the whole team
OL,13,Finvolved and especially to our
OL,14,Fpatients, whose feedback has helped
OL,15,Fshape this new way of delivering care."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@gO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778159474
OL,3,CWest Country man one of the first in
OL,4,Cthe UK to receive new cancer jab
OL,6,FJon Standing, Director of Pharmacy at
OL,7,FUniversity Hospitals Bristol and
OL,8,FWeston NHS Foundation Trust said:
OL,9,F"These new forms of subcutaneous
OL,10,Fimmunotherapy allow hospital pharmacy
OL,11,Fservices to focus on manufacturing and
OL,12,Fpreparing other forms of cancer
OL,13,Ftherapies.
OL,15,F"This helps patients receive their
OL,16,Fcancer treatments as quickly as
OL,17,Fpossible and follows the strategic
OL,18,Fapproach of the NHS to increase the
OL,19,Fcapacity to deliver cancer medicines."
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778159474
OL,3,CWest Country man one of the first in
OL,4,Cthe UK to receive new cancer jab
OL,6,FHealth and Social Care Secretary Wes
OL,7,FStreeting said: "Our National Cancer
OL,8,FPlan promised to do more and go faster
OL,9,Ffor patients ` already we are
OL,10,Fdelivering that change.
OL,12,F"As a cancer survivor, I know how
OL,13,Fimportant quick treatment is, and this
OL,14,Frollout will offer quicker, more
OL,15,Fconvenient care, saving patients time
OL,16,Fand helping them in their recovery
OL,17,Fwith less time in hospital.
OL,26,@oD@QOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778159474
OL,3,CWest Country man one of the first in
OL,4,Cthe UK to receive new cancer jab
OL,6,F"Not only that - it'll also free up
OL,7,Fvaluable time so clinicians can care
OL,8,Ffor even more people and potentially
OL,9,Fsave even more lives.
OL,11,F"The government is providing the
OL,12,Fhealth service with record funding,
OL,13,Faround 40,000 more people are starting
OL,14,Ftreatment on time, and rates of early
OL,15,Fdiagnosis are hitting record highs.
OL,17,F"Through innovations like this, we're
OL,18,Fmaking every penny and every second
OL,19,Fcount, and ensuring patients get NHS
OL,20,Fcare that fits around their lives, not
OL,21,Fthe other way around."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
